	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Aug 31st 1:18 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.71]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Get this question in-game alot. So here I will list where I hunted at what levels. Others<br>may certainly have other places, but all I can share is what I know.<br><br>level of Invectus: 31 Wizard<br>time playing Invectus: 48 days 21 hours+<br><br>level | hunting grounds<br>1-4 N.Qeynos solo<br><br>5-6 Qeynos Hills solo<br><br>7-9 Q.Hills, <br>Blackburrow, <br>Everfrost,<br>WK, <br>Paw(the old one, obviously) <br>- ALL solo and grouped<br><br>10-11 WK & Blackburrow - grouped<br><br>12-15 WK(mostly bandits),<br>Blackburrow, <br>NK(all beetles & griffawns), <br>Permafrost (group) <br>& Upper Guk(just 3 days), <br>Smugglers in Qeynos Sewers<br>- All grouped or 1 partner<br><br>16-18 Oasis (Massive Orc battles) & Unrest - FULL group, <br>Everfrost - grouped in the Tundra<br>Lavastorm - solo<br><br>19-22 Highpass - gnolls with 1 partner and grouped<br><br>23-27 Beholder(minos & eyes - grouped), <br>Lake Rathe(Aviak Guards - solo & grouped), <br>SK(Aviaks & Centaurs- solo & grouped), <br>Najena & Unrest- grouped, <br>Permafrost - grouped, <br>Upper Guk - grouped, Cazic - grouped, <br>Rathe Mts - solo & grouped, <br>OOT - Goblin Isle - grouped<br>Everfrost - Redwind's temple - grouped<br><br>28-30 Rathe Mts - Cyclops - grouped,<br>Rathe Mts - Giant Skels - solo, <br>Rathe Mts Troll Tower & HG's- FULL group(most others were much higher than me), <br>SK(Aviaks & outside Paw) - solo & grouped, <br>Najena, Paw, Unrest, Upper Guk, Cazic & Sol A - grouped, <br>OOT - Goblin Isle solo, <br>Everfrost - Redwind's temple - grouped<br>Beholder - Evil Eye lords - solo<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Invectus Stormborn<br>57 Evoker<br>Leader of <br>A'dileab de Paegen<br>Tunare Server</td></tr>
