	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f96785156819556><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=11&mid=96785156819556>RE: Where to hunt lvl 1 to 30</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=11&mid=96785156819556#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Sep 1st 7:39 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.66]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Don't forget that starting at about 11th level you can start hunting wisps.&nbsp;&nbsp;These are found just about everwhere but the best place to find them is the island in Erud's crossing somtimes called wisp island.  Not only are they good exp but the lightstones and Greater Lightstones are great when sold and are part of a quest involving the Gypsies in NK which leads to even more exp and better loot from the macial tomes recieved.  Stones are light weighing in at 0.1 stones so take seven backpacks and grab as many stones as you can before making a trip.  I've gained a full level from hunting wisps then gone and turned all the stones I had a the gypsies and BAM! I had my next level.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
